<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #5c48ee;
            --secondary-color-dark: #0f1e6a;
            --secondary-color: #f9fafe;
            --text-color: #333333;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --max-width: 1200px
        }

        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppin', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        nav {
            max-width: var(--max-width);
            margin: auto;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .navbar-logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            transition: .3s;
        }

        .navbar-logo:link {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .navbar-links {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .link a {
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 750;
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .link a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .link .navbar-btn {
            padding: .5rem 2rem;
            color: var(--white);
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .link .navbar-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color-dark);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: var(--max-width);
            margin: auto;
            padding: 1rem;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 100px);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 5rem;
        }

        .content-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .content-container h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 3.5rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color-dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .heading-1 {
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .heading-2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .content-container p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .image_container {
            position: relative;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            place-content: center;
        }

        .image_container img {
            width: 120%;
            max-width: 375px;
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .image_container img:nth-child(1) {
            transform: translateY(50px);
        }

        .image_container img:nth-child(2) {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
    </style>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hacktiv Learn</title>
</head>

<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="navbar-logo"><a href="/"> HacktivLearn </a></div>
        <ul class="navbar-links">
            <li class="link"><a href="/"> Home </a></li>
            <li class="link"><a href="/categories"> Category </a></li>
            <li class="link"><a href="/courses"> Courses </a></li>
            <li class="link"><a href="/profiles"> Profile </a></li>
            <li class="link"><a href="/login" class="navbar-btn"> Login </a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <section class="container">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h1>
                HacktivLearn <br>
                <span class="heading-1"> Educational Platform </span> <br>
                <span class="heading-2"> in The World </span>
            </h1>
            <p>
                HacktivLearn is an educational platform that helps you to learn everything in the world.
                This platform helps you to learn effectively by immersive learning environments that combines
                interactive lessons, virtual classrooms, and 1-on-1 learning. Open your horizons of knowledge
                from now with Us!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="image_container">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4145190/pexels-photo-4145190.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-julia-m-cameron-4145190.jpg&fm=jpg"
                alt="header">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6517078/pexels-photo-6517078.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600"
                alt="header">
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>